  "title": "Account Management/ Business Development Executive #80118",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Digital Resources Solutions Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Account Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Kaki Bukit</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Monday – Friday (9am – 6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Explore and pursue new commercial prospects within designated industries and sectors.</li><li>Cultivate and maintain strong rapport with current clients to enhance satisfaction and long-term loyalty.</li><li>Showcase and promote for the company’s offerings to both prospective and existing customers.</li><li>Work closely with cross-functional teams to deliver customized solutions aligned with client expectations.</li><li>Drive revenue and business expansion by actively managing accounts and initiating growth strategies.</li><li>Stay informed on industry developments, customer behaviours, and competitive activities.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma holder.</li><li>Excellent verbal, written, and interpersonal communication skills.</li><li>Highly motivated, enthusiastic, and demonstrates willingness to learn.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply, training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80118 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
